  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 2013, Gujarat based Akshar Spintex Limited is a company engaged in the manufacturing of cotton yarn. The company manufactures 100% cotton yarn which includes combed, semi-combed and carded yarn. </p><p>The manufacturing facility of the Company is situated in the vicinity of the rich cotton growing areas of Gujarat. The company has installed capacity of total 24,480 spindles.</p><p>The company has 216 employees on its payroll.</p>"
  },
